<div class="warning-box">
    <strong>⚠️ Accessibility Issues in This Form:</strong>
    <ul>
        <li>❌ No &lt;form&gt; element</li>
        <li>❌ Labels not associated with inputs (no for/id connection)</li>
        <li>❌ Radio buttons not in a fieldset with legend</li>
        <li>❌ Checkboxes not properly labeled</li>
        <li>❌ Submit is a div, not a button (can't activate with Enter/Space)</li>
        <li>❌ Date field has tabindex="-1" (removed from keyboard navigation)</li>
        <li>❌ Low contrast text (#aaa on white)</li>
        <li>❌ "Click here" link relies only on mouse onclick</li>
        <li>❌ No required field indicators for screen readers</li>
        <li>❌ No error handling or validation feedback</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Try it:</strong> Use only your keyboard (Tab key) to navigate this form and notice the problems!</p>
</div>
